17enum {
18 VP8D_NOFILTERING = 0,
19 VP8D_DEBLOCK = 1 << 0,
20 VP8D_DEMACROBLOCK = 1 << 1,
21 VP8D_ADDNOISE = 1 << 2,
22 VP8D_MFQE = 1 << 3
23};

25typedef struct {
26 int post_proc_flag;

28 int noise_level;
29 int display_ref_frame_flag;
30 int display_mb_modes_flag;
31 int display_b_modes_flag;
32 int display_mv_flag;
33} vp8_ppflags_t;
